                <note>3.4 Cancer … of others 4.3] <hi rend="italic">crossed pencil</hi></note>
                <note>3.12 If the males … females. 3.15] <hi rend="italic">scored blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note>6.1 I am … remarkable 6.8] <hi rend="italic">crossed blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note><hi rend="italic">Top of letter</hi>: ‘Use | Keep for Dom Animals’ <hi rend="italic">pencil</hi>;<ref target="#foot.f7"/> ‘Male <hi rend="italic">larger</hi> than ♀ | inequality &amp; size of Chelæ’ <hi rend="italic">blue crayon</hi></note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
